s2186: Zhao Dao Xiang Wang Yan first year
s2192: Four. Seventh month, locusts covered all under heaven. Commoners paid grain one thousand dan, bestowed rank one level.
s2195: Two. Crown prince from hostage Qin returned.
s2197: Twelve. Zhao pulled our Wu Sui, Fang Cheng.
s2201: Five. Meng Ao took Wei Suan Zao twenty cities. First established Dong Jun.
s2202: Wei Jing Min Wang first year. Qin pulled our twenty cities.
s2204: Three. Zhao chancellor, Wei chancellor met at Ke, allied.
s2206: Thirteen. Ju Xin died in Zhao.
s2210: Six. Five states together struck Qin.
s2211: Two. Qin pulled our Chao Ge. Wei moved from Pu Yang to Ye Wang.
s2214: Twenty-two. King moved east to Shou Chun, named Ying.
s2219: Seven. Comet appeared north west. Xia Tai Hou died. Meng Ao died.
s2228: Eight. Lao Ai enfeoffed Chang Xin Hou.
s2237: Nine. Comet appeared, across heaven. Lao Ai made disorder, moved his retainers to Shu. Comet again appeared.
s2238: Five. Qin pulled our Yuan, Pu Yang, Yan.
s2241: Twenty-five. Li Yuan assassinated Chun Shen Jun.
